spec_data.Name: gnat-srpm-macros
spec_data.Description:
This package contains RPM macros that need to be available when source RPM
packages that need the GNAT tools are built. It is a standalone package in
order to have as few dependencies as possible.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Tue 01 Aug 2017 04:08:00 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: RPM macros needed when source packages that need GNAT are built
